author: chris-dollin
msg: Added class GraphUtil and one method (so far), findAll( Graph ), which
is equivalent to find( ANY, ANY, ANY ).
Allowed find(S,P,O) to allow ANY instead of null.
Modified the Selector interface so that it exposes plausible S, P, and O
values. This is an API change.
We will be simplifying TripleMatch to reduce it to a very simple match.
